These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-1::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: november, october, may, june
1. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the person who's birthday is in june##1
2. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
3. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1  |    2    |    3    |  4   |
| Birthday   | may | october | november | june |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-2::.
There are 4 different nationalities: french, british, thai, indian
1. the indian is on the far right##1
2. the french is on the far left##1
3. the thai is on the right of the french##1

.:: Answer ::.
|       |  1   |   2   |     3      |   4    |
| Nationality   | french | thai | british | indian |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-3::.
There 4 different types of food: lettuce, lemon, spinach, blueberry
1. the person eating spinach is on the left of the person eating lettuce##1
2. the person eating lemon is on the left of the person eating blueberry##1
3. the person eating lemon is on the right of the person eating lettuce##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |   2    |      3      |       4       |
| Food   | spinach | lettuce | lemon | blueberry |

