.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-4::.
4 different pets are kept: rabbit, mouse, fish, bird
1. the owner of the fish is on the far left##1
2. the owner of the bird is on the far right##1
3. the owner of the mouse is on the left of the owner of the bird##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |  2   |    3    |  4  |
| Pet   | fish | rabbit | mouse | bird |

