1. the person driving the motorbike is on the far left##1
2. the person driving the trike is on the far right##1
3. the person driving the train is on the left of the person driving the trike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2    |    3    |    4     |
| Transport   | motorbike | van | train | trike |

