.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-1-6::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: soul, punk, gospel, blues
1. the fan of soul is on the far right##1
2. the fan of soul is on the right of the fan of punk##1
3. the fan of punk is on the right of the fan of gospel##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |      3       |     4     |
| Music-Genre   | blues | gospel | punk | soul |

