2. the person who likes aquamarine is on the left of the person who likes brown##1
3. the person who likes chestnut is on the left of the person who likes aquamarine##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |  2   |   3    |     4     |
| Color   | chestnut | aquamarine | brown | green |

